tan and is Pakistan's main source of water for industry and drinking; where does it rise?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\n\"One of Australia's oldest and most important industrial disputes and the subject of Henry Lawson's poem \"\"Freedom on the Wallaby\"\", in 1891 brought central Queensland to the brink of civil war. What group of people was involved?\"\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nA clapperboard is used in which industry?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nThe 2013-4 MacRobertson Shield international competition, hosted in New Zealand, was in what sport?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nThe main international cricket competitions are Test matches, ODI, and which other?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nIn the culinary world, what word is used for the edible offal of a fowl, typically including the heart, gizzard and liver?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nRedfoo and Sky Blu were members of which electronic rock band?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nWhat is the name of a book where photographs or stamps are kept?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nThe third part of trilogy of Hobbit movies, released at the end of 2014, is called what?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nNankey Poo, Poo Bah and Pish Tush are characters in which show?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nThe cocktail called a Tom Collins consists of lemon or lime juice, sugar, soda water and what else?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nBjrn Ulvaeus and Benny Andersson wrote most of the songs for which pop group?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nMarat, Robespierre, Danton are names associated with what event at the end of the 18th century?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nWhat is the name of the hand signalling system used by bookmakers to convey horses' odds?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nWhat is next in the sequence: Lima, Quito, Bogota...?\n\n### Response:\n", "### Instruction:\nThe winner of the Academy